snippet: Serena Williams turned heads when she made a cameo in Beyonce's "Sorry" music video — where she twerked heavily — and now the tennis star is releasing her own dancing video....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams turned heads when she made a cameo in Beyonce's "Sorry" music video — where she twerked heavily — and now the tennis star is releasing her own dancing video.
